  "3032230": {
    "name": "Mushiverse - Online Boardgame",
    "steam_appid": 3032230,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/89122f95a6f2a7abed19d2533e2780c7.poster.avif?t=1731949456\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/89122f95a6f2a7abed19d2533e2780c7.webm?t=1731949456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/89122f95a6f2a7abed19d2533e2780c7.mp4?t=1731949456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Mushiverse 是一款在线桌面游戏，可以由4到6名玩家进行游戏。<br></li><li> 凭借其独特的角色、村庄和机制，为您提供独一无二的体验。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/17ab9dcc7b9a8e2b4a8a93666a5a36d8.avif?t=1731949456\" width=624 height=124 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 你可以通过定制的角色轻松击败对手。<br></li><li> 你可以选择支付更少的租金来领先，或者把对手送进监狱并破坏他们，从而达到欢乐的巅峰。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/b6092c6cadd8841281c86fd9d78a52f0.poster.avif?t=1731949456\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/b6092c6cadd8841281c86fd9d78a52f0.webm?t=1731949456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/b6092c6cadd8841281c86fd9d78a52f0.mp4?t=1731949456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/b8daec94835c97fe82b428b578bf59b7.avif?t=1731949456\" width=624 height=124 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 作为一个违反游戏规则的角色，你可以激怒你的对手。当你在游戏中选择一个对手时，你会偷走他们的村庄和角色。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/c2b987ad83c8d7c6bfb9f27bf563f8b7.avif?t=1731949456\" width=624 height=124 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 在Mushiverse宇宙中，每个村庄都有其独特的特点。<br></li><li> 通过选择一个村庄，你选择你的队友并确定你的策略。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/77df3f2e3b8c08d67bacc4e04bfa9eb4.avif?t=1731949456\" width=624 height=124 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>地震机制</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 随机选择的城市被宣布为地震城市。<br></li><li> 地震城市的租金系数增加！<br></li><li> 注意！你可能想投资这个城市，但随时可能发生地震！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/9a2649cabe2373a1316ac01efe3576b0.poster.avif?t=1731949456\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/9a2649cabe2373a1316ac01efe3576b0.webm?t=1731949456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/9a2649cabe2373a1316ac01efe3576b0.mp4?t=1731949456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>恋爱中的城市</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 随机选择的两个城市互相坠入爱河。<br></li><li> 你在任何一个恋爱中的城市进行的操作会自动反映到另一个城市！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/7ff40d5e789870915d53c923b04179cb.poster.avif?t=1731949456\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/7ff40d5e789870915d53c923b04179cb.webm?t=1731949456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/7ff40d5e789870915d53c923b04179cb.mp4?t=1731949456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>农场系统</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 如果你在每个购买的地产上至少有一栋房子，你将开始从该地产获得被动收入。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/0d492bd35e85d31f7452d8c28900464f.poster.avif?t=1731949456\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/0d492bd35e85d31f7452d8c28900464f.webm?t=1731949456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/0d492bd35e85d31f7452d8c28900464f.mp4?t=1731949456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/0d39c4f41f32a93dc88aa5dacc19ae24.poster.avif?t=1731949456\" width=624 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/0d39c4f41f32a93dc88aa5dacc19ae24.webm?t=1731949456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/0d39c4f41f32a93dc88aa5dacc19ae24.mp4?t=1731949456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
